item.title: Adding bankbooth
item.dc:creator: @elweb elweb
item.description:
@elweb wrote:

-ADDING THE BANKBOOTHS-
go into client.java and search objects, you will find a list of already added object probably
after the last one hit enter at the end of itto creat a space then type in
objectxX(3217, 3419, 2213, 2);
the 3317 is the bank booth id
the 3419, 2213 are the coords
the 2 is the way it wil face, 2 and 4 will make it face south/north and 1 and 3 will make it face west/east
save and compile
